text: Dimpal Kumari Jha (; 12 July 1979 â€“ 24 April 2022) was a Nepalese politician. She was a member of the Provincial Assembly of Province No. 2. She was nominated as a Proportional representation member to participate in the Provincial Assembly of Province No. 2. She was a member of the Rastriya Janata Party Nepal. She also was a member of the 2013 Nepalese Constituent Assembly.
